 2023-02352023-03-16PMO
ActRoyal Canadian Mounted Police Act
PrecisAppointment of MICHAEL ROBERT DUHEME of Ottawa, Ontario, to be Commissioner of the Royal Canadian Mounted Police, on an interim basis, to hold office during pleasure, for a term of two years or until such time as a new Commissioner is appointed, whichever occurs first, effective March 18, 2023.
